/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太耐無聯絡 唔知佢變成點 唔知佢出左pool未 唔知佢會唔會覺得我好煩<br />\n而家大學畢埋業出左黎做野 有時見到佢update facebook都會諗起佢<br />\n男仔最難忘既未必係初戀 而係佢第一個暗戀 而最後又得唔到既女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87632756fbdf82288a213e6366f812599390852f","tid":1009122,"uid":125755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"之前暗戀左一個男仔，仲未表白佢就已經轉工無再有聯繫<br />\n<br />\n無見兩年再遇返，佢竟然第一眼就認到我，好想去馬但唔知點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4b9257f9883f01acd1e1282f622369ed1bd0fc","tid":1009122,"uid":38630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98ba33d20181594501484dda5e805ddf66755f1d","tid":1009122,"uid":161185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1b1f8a882122c586c94d9a6221ceed0baf95720","tid":1009122,"uid":38630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548e089b1b8d650d0dccdd22d85abedb8e0f8eb9","tid":1009122,"uid":161185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"久唔久就記起有呢個人同佢個名，但其實都已經唔係好記得個樣，更唔好講話隔左成廿年，就算見到都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"原來大家都係大海撈針<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係搵緊一個曾經係記憶存在過嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:04:53.000Z","msg":"希望有一日大家都搵得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"大家咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487d39d954d5b7be37a20e8fa091c27f1af784e3","tid":1009122,"uid":38630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50412adff64dab4917d5fa9459b1897e4630cc80","tid":1009122,"uid":147892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cited